title: The Jack Fairman
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegan items on the menu include the freedom salad, jacket potato with beans, side salad (w/ no dressing) and the sweet potato, chickpea & spinach curry with extra poppadums (instead of naan bread), vegetable samosas, and large onion bhajis. Thursday is curry night. Broadcasts live news, licensed outside area, music in the evening, TV screens, free Wi-Fi. Has a huge variety of alcoholic drinks.
